oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Group of people on rock
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A group of people, including several girls, a couple, a child, and men in hats, stand on Bee Rock, Monterey, Tennessee. Several trees are growing at the top. The photograph is from a distance and shows the height of the rock.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
